## Integration with @pmf-analyst

- **@pmf-analyst** reads your latest `brainstorm-analysis/*.md` for the same **Country** when present and extends Phase 4 triangulation with a **Customer Ideation Hub (106)** column
- You do **not** run Braun & Clarke on behalf of **@pmf-analyst**; you produce a **prior** structured input so **@pmf-analyst** can merge themes in its own phases

## Integration with orchestrator

- **Regional E2E:** Optional **Step 5** after **105** SME (**Step 7**) and **105** Customer (**Step 8**), when `research/brainstorm-sessions/` contains in-scope P&T or ideation files; **skip** if **105** outputs are missing or P&T sources are absent
- Log output path + mission ID in **MISSION_LOG.md** when orchestrated

